{"tid":277823,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"接唔接受到大你4年嘅女仔。分手後半個月你已經有第二個","createTime":"2017-06-10T03:15:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-10T09:32:15.000Z","uid":9524,"like":2,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"06195985b3b9b88dff9411cf282fdc07edee9813","tid":277823,"uid":9524,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T03:15:48.000Z","msg":"講下雙方背景先<br />\n男方：19，中學未畢業<br />\n女方：23，下年大學畢業，出國讀書<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 喺真愛<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 條女收兵，根本無可能<br />\n再補充下：<br />\n佢之前去比賽就認識咗依個女仔，<br />\n戈陣我仲未同佢分手，不過都冷戰緊，<br />\n結果佢去完番嚟就同我分手，<br />\n大約半個月後朋友send左張圖比我睇，<br />\n佢入左醫院，有句說話喺多謝個女仔，煲左湯比佢飲，<br />\n再到今日我睇個女仔ig<br />\n個女仔話，再走多步結局就會不一樣<br />\n而我又見到留言到有個人話唔喺唔走多步呀？<br />\n而留言戈個人都喺有份去比賽，所以好肯定ex喺追緊佢<br />\n條女facebook post好多一大班人影嘅相，<br />\n唯獨係同我ex影嘅係單獨照亦都喺唯一一張。<br />\n不過真個唔甘心輸比個咁大又唔係靚嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08d3802d093216b372f45f88d50cd7a92b901ad7","tid":277823,"uid":45508,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T03:31:06.000Z","msg":"戈你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e164a0aa5face7c84e20f0ac08f0b08fc8288431","tid":277823,"uid":76527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T03:31:31.000Z","msg":"個負評係俾你，唔關投票事"},{"pid":"ff518989b3cce74f8e9ce43c316585f061e74e6d","tid":277823,"uid":9524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T03:34:07.000Z","msg":"對唔住囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebfcfb95d2767f33e5a7ed8f0dda6864e13b72a5","tid":277823,"uid":5588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T03:37:42.000Z","msg":"19歲仲讀緊中學<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ac88a9743eae893b2c5d3041b8fc5fa80d1cd66","tid":277823,"uid":110207,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"